00:03:01,479 --> 00:03:05,799
in order for it to be

67
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:12,519
valid or in order for it to be correct.

68
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:15,680
The author then mentions at-Tasmiyah.

69
00:03:12,519 --> 00:03:18,319
And this is a point of contention

70
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:21,120
