00:03:27,879 --> 00:03:34,799
mukammilatil Wudu. It is something that

76
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:37,879
is ideal for the Wudu.

77
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:40,840
If we were to really look at the at the

78
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:44,959
evidence for this,

79
