93
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:35,759
Allah's name on the wudu.

94
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:37,560
Now, if the narration is authentic and

95
00:04:35,759 --> 00:04:39,639
if it's clear,

96
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:42,839
then why exactly is it a point of

97
00:04:39,639 --> 00:04:45,360
contention amongst the scholars?

98
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:48,479
Right? You would imagine that

99
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:51,520
if the narration is authentic

100
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:53,040
and if it's clear this,

101
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:55,680
you would imagine that they would all

102
