Many view this narration as being weak.

106
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:10,560
But another reason is

107
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:13,639
that there are other instances in which

108
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:16,639
the Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam's

109
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:16,639
actions

110
00:05:16,839 --> 00:05:23,679
actually contradict this narration.

111
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:27,320
So, for instance, just

112
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:29,759
one example of this, a companion

113
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:32,879
came upon the Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi

114
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:35,839
