00:05:56,879 --> 00:05:59,480
Bismillah.

124
00:05:58,279 --> 00:06:02,199
Correct?

125
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:04,560
So, this is what for instance in the

126
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:06,479
Hanafi madhhab they cite as a

