146
00:06:58,279 --> 00:07:04,639
It's most comprehensive and inclusive.

147
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:06,160
So, a person says Bismillah ma al-dhikr.

148
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:09,560
When is

149
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:11,880
saying Bismillah obligatory? It's

150
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:13,879
obligatory when a person remembers. If a

151
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:15,800
